data.description: Welcome to this charming ranch-style brick home! As you enter, you'll be greeted with a delightful, enclosed porch, perfect for relaxing evenings. This well-maintained gem offers two spacious bedrooms and a well-appointed bathroom. The large living room is flooded with natural light through its expansive windows, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The generous kitchen features ample counter space, a convenient pantry, and an adjoining dining area, making it perfect for everyday meals. The laundry area adds convenience to your daily routine. Step outside to the sizable backyard, where you'll find plenty of space for outdoor activities and relaxation. The detached one-car garage provides convenient parking and additional storage. This home is ready for you to move in and start creating wonderful memories. Don't miss the opportunity to make this delightful property your own! Roof updated 2019, windows updated 2019, new water heater.
